<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_58872_needit.GetManager1</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>GetManager1</name><script><![CDATA[var GetManager1 = Class.create();
// Extend the global.AbstractAjaxProcessor class
GetManager1.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor,{
    // Define the getMgr function.      
    getMgr: function() {
		// Create a GlideRecord for the User table.
        var userRecord = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
		// Use the sysparm_userID passed from the client side to retrieve a record from the User table.
        userRecord.get(this.getParameter('sysparm_userID'));
		// Return the Manager for the requested record
        return userRecord.manager.getDisplayValue() + '';
    },
    type: 'GetManager1'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-08-23 22:03:19</sys_created_on><sys_id>a8f1a15e2f387110f1c757892799b632</sys_id><sys_mod_count>13</sys_mod_count><sys_name>GetManager1</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NeedIt" source="x_58872_needit">6ead8e780f603200cd674f8ce1050ed1</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="NeedIt">6ead8e780f603200cd674f8ce1050ed1</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_a8f1a15e2f387110f1c757892799b632</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-08-29 19:00:07</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
